PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1779109902
OL,3,CGordon Lyons says Sinn Fein waging 'co-
OL,4,Cordinated attack' over street signs
OL,6,FThe DUP Communities Minister has
OL,7,Faccused Sinn Fein of using funding
OL,8,Funcertainty around a street signs
OL,9,Ftranslation project to wage a
OL,10,F"coordinated attack" against him.
OL,12,FGordon Lyons claimed it was based on a
OL,13,F"fabrication".
OL,15,FThe minister made the claim during
OL,16,Frobust exchanges with Sinn Fein
OL,17,Fmembers of his Assembly scrutiny
OL,18,Fcommittee including chairman Colm
OL,19,FGildernew ` who likened the minister
OL,20,Fto an arsonist who blames the fire
OL,21,Fbrigade for causing water damage.
OL,26,@kD@YrroD@OrrrD@AOUrD@TO]uD@AOUuD@MO]xD@
OL,26,A]rr
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1779109902
OL,3,CGordon Lyons says Sinn Fein waging 'co-
OL,4,Cordinated attack' over street signs
OL,6,FThe clashes played out as Mr Lyons
OL,7,Fappeared before the committee to face
OL,8,Fquestions on the future of the
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland Place-Name Project.
OL,11,FThe academic initiative based at
OL,12,FQueen's University researches the
OL,13,Forigins of street names and also
OL,14,Fprovides councils support in
OL,15,Ftranslating English street names into
OL,16,FIrish.
OL,18,FSinn Fein MLAs have accused Mr Lyons
OL,19,Fof refusing to renew funding for the
OL,20,Fproject this year.
OL,26,@kD@YrrzD@Grr
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1779109902
OL,3,CGordon Lyons says Sinn Fein waging 'co-
OL,4,Cordinated attack' over street signs
OL,6,FHowever, the minister has rejected
OL,7,Fthat claim, insisting the work had
OL,8,Fpreviously been funded by the Sinn
OL,9,FFein-led Department of Finance and he
OL,10,Fhas made no proactive decision to cut
OL,11,Ffinancial support for the scheme.
OL,13,FMr Lyons told the committee that when
OL,14,Fit became clear DoF was not going to
OL,15,Fcontinue its financial support this
OL,16,Fyear he put in contingency
OL,17,Farrangements to allow it to continue
OL,18,Foperating into the summer pending
OL,19,Fexamination of other options aimed at
OL,20,Fsecuring its future.
OL,26,@kD@YrrqD@Brr
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1779109902
OL,3,CGordon Lyons says Sinn Fein waging 'co-
OL,4,Cordinated attack' over street signs
OL,6,FHowever, he said the project has since
OL,7,Fbeen hit by resourcing and staffing
OL,8,Fissues within the university, with
OL,9,Fsome team members having decided to
OL,10,Fmove on.
OL,12,FThe minister noted that Sinn Fein
OL,13,FEconomy minister Caoimhe Archibald had
OL,14,Fsignalled an intent to step in and
OL,15,Fsupport the project but he said his
OL,16,Fministerial colleague had not yet
OL,17,Foffered "details on the nature or
OL,18,Fscope of the proposed support".
OL,26,@kD@YrrtD@_rryD@IOUzD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1779109902
OL,3,CGordon Lyons says Sinn Fein waging 'co-
OL,4,Cordinated attack' over street signs
OL,6,F"We remain open to engagement with
OL,7,Fcolleagues across government to
OL,8,Fidentify a way forward," he said.
OL,10,FMr Lyons' version of events drew
OL,11,Fcriticism from Sinn Fein committee
OL,12,Fmembers, with deputy chairwoman Cathy
OL,13,FMason claiming his approach to the
OL,14,Fproject fitted a pattern of hostility
OL,15,Ftoward Irish language initiatives.
OL,26,@kD@YrrnD@AOUpD@XO]sD@Vrr
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1779109902
OL,3,CGordon Lyons says Sinn Fein waging 'co-
OL,4,Cordinated attack' over street signs
OL,6,F"We've got place names (project),
OL,7,Fyou're embroiled in court cases
OL,8,Fagainst the Irish language, you've
OL,9,Fremoved the (Irish language) branding
OL,10,Ffrom your department, you're clearly
OL,11,Fblocking the development of an Irish
OL,12,Flanguage strategy," she said.
OL,14,F"You've got form on this, with one
OL,15,Fthing after another. Why are you so
OL,16,Fafraid of the Irish language and Irish
OL,17,Fidentity?"
OL,19,FShe added: "Minister, with all due
OL,20,Frespect, you're judged on your
OL,21,Factions, not not empty words on this.
OL,26,@kD@YrrnD@AOUtD@SO]vD@AOUyD@JO]{D@LOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1779109902
OL,3,CGordon Lyons says Sinn Fein waging 'co-
OL,4,Cordinated attack' over street signs
OL,6,F"Is it not the truth that you pulled
OL,7,Fthis funding because you're terrified
OL,8,Fthat there was 2,400 applications in
OL,9,FBelfast alone, 990 of them are being
OL,10,Fprogressed and suddenly this support
OL,11,Fjust disappears.
OL,13,F"Is that incompetence or is that
OL,14,Fdeliberate contempt?"
OL,16,FMr Lyons said "all of the facts and
OL,17,Fevidence" showed he had not cut
OL,18,Ffunding for the project.
OL,26,@kD@YrrnD@AOUuD@AOUvD@UO]xD@OOUyD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1779109902
OL,3,CGordon Lyons says Sinn Fein waging 'co-
OL,4,Cordinated attack' over street signs
OL,6,FIn subsequent exchanges with Ms
OL,7,FMason's party colleague Maoliosa
OL,8,FMcHugh, the minister added: "I believe
OL,9,Fthat this is a coordinated attack
OL,10,Faround this issue."
OL,12,FHe continued: "Many representatives of
OL,13,Fyour party have said that I cut
OL,14,Ffunding for this project, and that is
OL,15,Fjust wrong, and it's disappointing
OL,16,Fthat the evidence has been produced
OL,17,Ftoday and people still fail to grasp
OL,18,Fthat."
OL,26,@kD@YrrpD@]OUrD@SO]tD@OOUzD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1779109902
OL,3,CGordon Lyons says Sinn Fein waging 'co-
OL,4,Cordinated attack' over street signs
OL,6,FMr Gildernew challenged the minister's
OL,7,Fcontention, stating he was "absolutely
OL,8,Fflabbergasted" by some of his claims.
OL,10,F"You remind me increasingly, minister,
OL,11,Flike the arsonist who's running around
OL,12,Ftrying to blame the fire brigade for
OL,13,Fcausing water damage," he said.
OL,15,F"You have an excuse for everything and
OL,16,Fa solution for nothing when it comes
OL,17,Fto the Irish language."
OL,26,@kD@YrroD@\OUpD@NO]rD@AOUuD@VO]wD@AOUyD@
OL,26,AWO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1779109902
OL,3,CGordon Lyons says Sinn Fein waging 'co-
OL,4,Cordinated attack' over street signs
OL,6,FMr Lyons said the committee chair's
OL,7,Fclaim that he had cut the project's
OL,8,Ffunding was a "fabrication and it had
OL,9,Fno basis in reality".
OL,11,F"Both the chair and the deputy chair
OL,12,Fput out statements saying that I had
OL,13,Fcut funding, and I don't know where
OL,14,Fthey got that from," he said.
OL,26,@kD@YrrpD@OOUqD@TO]sD@AOUvD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1779109902
OL,3,CGordon Lyons says Sinn Fein waging 'co-
OL,4,Cordinated attack' over street signs
OL,6,FThe minister added: "The fact is that
OL,7,FI did not cut any funding, but that
OL,8,Fdoesn't fit his (Mr Gildernew's)
OL,9,Fnarrative. And what the chair did was
OL,10,Fmake it up. He made it up. He said I
OL,11,Fcut funding. There's no evidence for
OL,12,Fthat. There's no basis for that.
OL,26,@kD@YrrnD@UOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1779109902
OL,3,CGordon Lyons says Sinn Fein waging 'co-
OL,4,Cordinated attack' over street signs
OL,6,F"There's no justification for him
OL,7,Fsaying that. He made it up to suit his
OL,8,Fown political narrative. And we have
OL,9,Fprovided the evidence today of how
OL,10,Fthat is not the case. And they're
OL,11,F(Sinn Fein) ignoring the reality
OL,12,Fbecause they have their own narrative
OL,13,Fthat they want to get out to distract,
OL,14,FI have to say, from their own failings.
OL,16,F"And this is becoming quite common now
OL,17,F` they just blame somebody else for
OL,18,Ftheir own failings."
OL,26,@kD@YrrnD@AOUsD@HrrxD@AOUzD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44713
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1779109902
OL,3,CGordon Lyons says Sinn Fein waging 'co-
OL,4,Cordinated attack' over street signs
OL,6,FMr Lyons continued: "I am, unlike
OL,7,Fyourself Mr Chairman, I have been
OL,8,Fhonest, and I've been telling the
OL,9,Ftruth on this issue, and I have not
OL,10,Ffabricated anything at all."
OL,12,FThe minister's DUP colleague Pam
OL,13,FCameron defended his handling of the
OL,14,Fissue and accused Sinn Fein of pushing
OL,15,F"lies" about Mr Lyons within the Irish
OL,16,Flanguage community for political gain.
OL,18,F"It's terrible, it's hateful, and it's
OL,19,Fhighly offensive to me," said the DUP
OL,20,Fcommittee member.
OL,26,@kD@YrrnD@UOUrD@\O]vD@YrrwD@AOUwD@FO]zD@
OL,26,AAOU{D@XO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44714
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1779109902
OL,3,CGordon Lyons says Sinn Fein waging 'co-
OL,4,Cordinated attack' over street signs
OL,6,F"I'm really offended by the slant put
OL,7,Fon me as unionist, quite frankly."
OL,9,FMr Lyons insisted he had "no hatred or
OL,10,Fcontempt for the Irish language".
OL,12,F"I'm used to unfortunately in this job
OL,13,Fbeing lied about and having things
OL,14,Fsaid about me that just simply aren't
OL,15,Ftrue in order to suit the political
OL,16,Fagendas of others," he said.
OL,18,F"Unfortunately that comes with the job.
OL,26,@kD@YrrnD@AOUoD@bO]qD@ZOUrD@`O]tD@AOUxD@
OL,26,ASO]zD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G14/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44715
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1779109902
OL,3,CGordon Lyons says Sinn Fein waging 'co-
OL,4,Cordinated attack' over street signs
OL,6,F"I think what has annoyed me more is
OL,7,Fthat even whenever evidence is
OL,8,Fprovided, when the facts are laid out,
OL,9,Fwhen my department has been open in
OL,10,Fproviding the information, others are
OL,11,Fdenying the reality that's in front of
OL,12,Fthem in black and white.
OL,14,F"That's something that I struggle with
OL,15,F` that people can't seem to accept the
OL,16,Ftruth of the matter, and that they're
OL,17,Fjust doubling down and doubling down
OL,18,Fagain and again.
OL,26,@kD@YrrnD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G15/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44716
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1779109902
OL,3,CGordon Lyons says Sinn Fein waging 'co-
OL,4,Cordinated attack' over street signs
OL,6,F"And if they think it's short-term
OL,7,Fpolitical gain, maybe it is, but long
OL,8,Fterm, it's not good for this place and
OL,9,Fit's not good for people out there
OL,10,Feither who want us to address issues.
OL,12,F"There will be significant areas of
OL,13,Fdisagreement that we have on issues
OL,14,Faround the Irish language and how it
OL,15,Fis dealt with in the public sphere.
OL,17,F"But it is particularly frustrating on
OL,18,Fthis issue when it is crystal clear
OL,19,Fwhat has happened, yet some are still
OL,20,Fusing it for political purposes.
OL,26,@kD@YrrnD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G16/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
